caption: Wellness With @elainerhayes 🌿 Meet Elaine Hayes — a wellness entrepreneur, life coach, and mama of two (soon to be three!). She’s passionate about helping women reconnect with their power and live vibrant, intentional lives. Elaine is the founder of Wellcraft, a holistic wellness platform offering over 300 on-demand Pilates classes, guided meditations, and mindset tools designed to meet women wherever they are—in body, mind, and soul. Read more about how she incorporates Juna into her daily routine on the blog!
